            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                    <strong>How do I create an account?</strong>
                </button>
            </h2>

            <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    <em>Select the Sign up button at the top right of the site and fill up the required details.</em>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                    <strong>I already have an account, how do I order?</strong>
                </button>
            </h2>

            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    <em>
                      <ol style="list-style-type:1">
                        <li>Select the product/s that you want through pressing the Add to Cart button.</li>
                        <li>To proceed to checkout, just click on the cart button at the top right of your screen then click the checkout button.</li>
                        <li>Enter your address and click Proceed to Payment.</li>
                        <li>Select your mode of payment from the choices below and the details of where you should send your payments will be shown.</li>
                        <li>Send your payment to the account then send a screenshot as proof of payment to the email shown.</li>
                        <li>Your order will now be processed.</li>
                      </ol>
                    </em>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
